  "text": "About Peroxidase immunostaining ofCB1 cells was carried out to show reactivity for intracellular antigens recognized by the rat anti-DC mAbs 2A1 [CITATION_1] and by the hamster anti-DC M342 [CITATION_2] kindly provided by N. Romani (University ofInnsbruck, Innsbruck, Austria). CBl cells were grown on coverslips and fixed in cold acetone . Cells were incubated for 1 h with mAbs in the presence of 1% normal mouse serum, washed and stained with peroxidase mouse anti-hamster (Pierce, Rockford, IL) or anti-rat Ig (Boehringer Mannheim), and visualized using diaminobenzidine as substrate (Sigma Chemical Co.).",
