      "span_text": "About Peroxidase immunostaining ofCB1 cells was carried out to show reactivity for intracellular antigens recognized by the rat anti-DC mAbs 2A1  and by the hamster anti-DC M342  kindly provided by N. Romani (University ofInnsbruck, Innsbruck, Austria)."
